Summary MARKETING COMMUNICATIONS / PUBLIC RELATIONS / INTERACTIVE AGENCY EXPERIENCE 

• Significant experience in marketing/communications, public relations, community relations and internal/external communications (including formal training in crisis communications); 
• Experience in print and digital communications; 
• Experience working with interactive agencies, both on the client and the agency sides. 

JOURNALISM / COMMUNICATIONS / PUBLISHING BACKGROUND 

• Formal education and extensive experience in journalistic writing, editing and photography;  
• Completed the prestigious University of Missouri-Columbia “Missouri Photo Workshop” in 1990; 
• Basic videography and editing skills. 

ORGANIC SEARCH OPTIMIZATION (SEO) / ONLINE REPUTATION MANAGEMENT (ORM) EXPERTISE 

• In-house and business-to-business agency SEO experience; 
• Domestic and international Web site experience;  
• Internet search marketing (pay-per-click) campaign management and analysis;  
• Corporate blog SEO and management best practices; 
• Online reputation management (ORM); 
• Extensive Hitwise competitive analysis system experience; 
• Understand importance of accessibility compliance and usability in Web site design. 

WEB ANALYTICS EXPERIENCE  

• WebTrends and Google Analytics; 
• Analytics reporting and maintenance;  
• Enterprise-level Content Management Systems (Microsoft, Ektron, VinSolutions); 
• Was trained personally by web analytics pioneer John Marshall, co-founder of internet marketing training firm Market Motive (www.marketmotive.com).  

SOCIAL MEDIA / BLOGGING 

• Understand role of user-generated content and social media sites, such as Facebook, LinkedIn, Twitter, Google+, PRWeb, Yelp, etc.;  
• Understand the importance of engaging audiences and building brands through content development on social media and blogs; 
• Online reputation management. 

PROJECT MANAGEMENT  

• Experience managing projects, archiving project assets, tracking milestones and team communication. Specialties:Digital communications -- organic search optimization, paid search engine marketing (PPC); landing page optimization; blog optimization; Web analytics, Web site competitive analysis; social media engagement; journalistic writing, editing and photography for Web and print; public relations; internal communications. Summary MARKETING COMMUNICATIONS / PUBLIC RELATIONS / INTERACTIVE AGENCY EXPERIENCE 

